Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:02.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(782,294)}艺术馆
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.83,0:01:04.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上流小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:04.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lady Upturn
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.21,0:01:06.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,您能再临我们的画廊  令我倍感荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:06.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Always a delight to have you back at our gallery
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,家里的艺术品我都看腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm bored by the art in my home
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.71,0:01:13.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有没有什么新奇又有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.71,0:01:13.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you have that's new and interesting?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.63,0:01:18.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我特地留了最新最上好的艺术品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.63,0:01:18.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, I've been saving our newest and finest pieces
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.18,0:01:19.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,供您欣赏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.18,0:01:19.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just for you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.39,0:01:22.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这幅作品是由我们一名新兴画家所作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:22.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This work is by one of our emerging artists
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.02,0:01:27.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从哪里新兴的  石头底下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:27.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where did they emerge from, under a rock?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.27,0:01:30.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.27,0:01:30.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.57,0:01:33.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上流小姐  我深感抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.57,0:01:33.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lady Upturn, I am so, so sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.99,0:01:36.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不该向您展示那幅垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.99,0:01:36.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should never have shown you that dreck
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.37,0:01:41.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:41.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never fear
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.70,0:01:45.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一样艺术保证让你激动不已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:45.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This next work is guaranteed to excite
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.12,0:01:50.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村第一舞剧团
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:50.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikini Bottom's premier dance troupe
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.59,0:01:52.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,创作出了一出全新舞剧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:52.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has created a performance so new
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.84,0:01:55.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就连他们自己都还不知道跳的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:55.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,even they don't know what it is yet
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.31,0:02:07.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟着音乐节奏动来动去早就不新了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:07.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Moving in time to music is hardly new
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.14,0:02:09.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一样对此无感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:09.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This does nothing for me, either
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.86,0:02:15.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里肯定会有你喜欢的艺术品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:15.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Surely, there's something here you'll enjoy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.28,0:02:17.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恐怕并不会有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:17.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I'm afraid not
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.53,0:02:18.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,瑞吉吉尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:18.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Regigilled
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.24,0:02:21.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要散个步  来放空思绪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:21.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need a walk to clear my mind
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.87,0:02:23.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,背着我走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:23.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Carry me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.03,0:02:24.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:24.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Very good, ma'am
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.41,0:02:29.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我失败惨重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:29.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alas, I have failed
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.90,0:03:01.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真抱歉  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.90,0:03:01.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My apologies, madam
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.78,0:03:05.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我应该马上带您远离这噪音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:05.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I shall remove your person from this cacophony at once
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.58,0:03:07.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用  瑞吉吉尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:07.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, Regigilled
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.20,0:03:08.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带我靠近点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:08.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take me closer
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.25,0:03:10.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如您所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:10.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.08,0:03:13.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那边那位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:13.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You, there
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.34,0:03:17.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有权在这里吹竖笛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:17.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm allowed to play my clarinet here
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.84,0:03:19.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里可是自由的海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:19.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a free ocean, you know
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.97,0:03:21.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我绝对不可能停
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:21.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not stopping
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.13,0:03:22.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:22.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.68,0:03:24.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不敢奢望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:24.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't dream of it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.43,0:03:28.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可是最有意思又前卫的音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:28.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is the most interesting and avant-garde music
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.35,0:03:30.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我多年以来闻所未闻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:30.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have heard in years
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.10,0:03:33.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太崇高了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:33.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is sublime
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.27,0:03:34.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有赞助者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:34.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you have a patron?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.40,0:03:36.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我务必要赞助你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:36.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I simply must be yours
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.77,0:03:38.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好好  太好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:38.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, very funny
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.78,0:03:39.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:39.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is this
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.24,0:03:42.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,藏了摄影机要拍个电视整人节目吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:42.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,one of those hidden-camera TV prank shows?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.28,0:03:43.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:43.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heavens, no
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.45,0:03:45.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,电视是最低级的艺术形式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:45.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Television is the lowest form of art
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,瑞吉吉尔德  给这位付钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Regigilled, pay the man
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.66,0:03:51.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不能拿钱来收买我这种天才的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:51.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't just buy the soul of a raw talent like myself
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.08,0:03:55.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小姐  你正好买到了个艺术家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:55.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lady, you just bought yourself an artist
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:58.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(600,438)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.46,0:04:01.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,废物们好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:01.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, losers
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.22,0:04:03.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:03.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.76,0:04:06.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你高兴个什么劲  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:06.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's with all the joy, Mr. Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.43,0:04:09.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在是个带薪音乐家了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:09.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a paid musician now
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.52,0:04:10.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:10.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.31,0:04:11.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,音乐家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:11.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Musician?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.48,0:04:12.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带薪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:12.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Paid?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.94,0:04:16.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随便你笑  反正是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:16.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Laugh all you want, but it's true
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.27,0:04:20.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也不用坐这只付最低工资的大牢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:20.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need this minimum-wage prison anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.90,0:04:22.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我辞职
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:22.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I quit
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.80,0:04:41.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥的梦想终于要成真了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:41.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward's dreams are finally coming true
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.81,0:04:52.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临你的新家  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:52.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to your new home, Mr. Tentacles
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.90,0:04:59.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:59.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my, it's incredible
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.61,0:05:01.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但你又要住哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:01.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But where are you going to live?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.57,0:05:05.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整栋豪宅都是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:05.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The mansion is mine
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.49,0:05:07.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你只能住一间小房间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:07.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just get one tiny room
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.78,0:05:11.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:11.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.45,0:05:15.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我等不及要炫耀你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:15.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I cannot wait to show you off
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.25,0:05:18.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给那些引领时尚的富豪朋友看了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:18.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to my wealthy, taste-making friends
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.17,0:05:19.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好马上开始作曲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:19.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so you better get writing
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.96,0:05:21.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:21.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am, ma'am
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.46,0:05:23.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  你这个天才
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:23.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Toodle-oo, you genius, you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:36.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(444,864)}鲈多芬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:36.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(990,864)}鳊姆斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:36.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1522,864)}龙虾拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:36.31,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 贝多芬              勃拉姆斯                 李伯拉斯\N德国音乐家         德国作曲家           美国钢琴家 ]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:44.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(570,576)}上流百货
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:22.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(730,442)}没错\N正在营业
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.95,0:06:37.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我让开  苦力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:37.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out of my way, peon
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.62,0:06:40.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真抱歉  大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:40.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So sorry, my lord
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.08,0:06:41.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:41.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.79,0:06:44.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真是  非常自信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:44.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was very, uh, confident of you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.71,0:06:45.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:45.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.55,0:06:49.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成为艺术家就需要有艺术家的气质
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:46.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Being an artist
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:49.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,requires having an artist's temperament
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.93,0:06:50.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:50.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you boob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.35,0:06:53.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干什么磨蹭这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:53.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What took you so long?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.93,0:06:56.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是过来邀请你们两位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:56.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, then, I'm only here to invite you both
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.97,0:06:59.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前来观赏我的盛大首秀音乐会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:59.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to my big debut concert
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.19,0:07:09.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,见证我在裤头村最宏伟的舞台重生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:06.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Witness my rebirth
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:09.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on the grandest stage in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.82,0:07:12.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前提是你们有假放
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:12.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you can get the time off
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.03,0:07:16.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他不知怎么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:16.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Somehow, he's even
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.04,0:07:18.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比以前上班时还要讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:18.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,more annoying now than when he worked here
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.66,0:07:19.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:19.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.96,0:07:22.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥之所以会这么讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:22.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward is just being insufferable
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.33,0:07:25.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是因为他的梦想都要成真了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:25.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because his dreams are coming true
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.13,0:07:26.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要过去支持他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:26.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have to go and support him
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.71,0:07:28.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们可是他朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:28.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're his friends
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.34,0:07:32.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朋友这俩字言过其实了  不过算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:32.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, "friends" is a strong word, but fine
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:36.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1134,510)}裤头村\N著名剧院
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:36.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1564,896)}今晚  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.43,0:07:40.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:40.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hiya, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.77,0:07:42.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟蟹老板想来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:42.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs and I just wanted to
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在你上场前祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wish you luck before your big show
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.56,0:07:46.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好运
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:46.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Luck?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.32,0:07:47.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:47.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.90,0:07:51.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可是世上最伟大的音乐家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:51.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the greatest musician who ever lived
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.24,0:07:53.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是富豪杂志说的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:53.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rich people say so
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:55.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(398,378)}富豪杂志\N世上最伟大的音乐家
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.70,0:07:57.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱确实有理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:57.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't argue with money
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.03,0:07:58.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去找你们的位子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:07:58.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, go find your seats
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.54,0:08:00.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在得准备上台
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:00.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm in the middle of my pre-show ritual
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.75,0:08:03.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可不能被打扰到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:03.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I don't want to be bothered
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.18,0:08:15.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚上好  各位音乐爱好者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:15.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good evening, music lovers
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.34,0:08:18.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想必各位跟我一样  已经厌倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:18.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like me, I'm sure you are tired of
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.10,0:08:22.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老一套把戏奏出的老一套音符
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:22.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the same old notes being played the same old ways
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.98,0:08:24.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请各位放心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:24.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, fear not
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.35,0:08:28.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚  你们终将听到全新的音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:28.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tonight you will finally hear something new
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.19,0:08:31.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚  为你们隆重介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:31.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tonight I present to you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.57,0:08:34.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:34.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Squidward Tentacles
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,忘却你们的婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget your wedding
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.75,0:08:44.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,忘却你们第一个子女的诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:44.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget the birth of your first child
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.67,0:08:46.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚必将是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:46.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is going to be
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.42,0:08:50.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这辈子最美好的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:50.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the greatest night of your lives
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.70,0:09:19.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多么动听啊  医生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:19.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't it dazzling, Doctor?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.29,0:09:28.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:28.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.46,0:09:30.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  上流小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:30.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, Lady Upturn
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.84,0:09:31.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是否可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:31.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May I?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.80,0:09:33.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然了  鱼伯格医生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:33.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course, Dr. Fishberg
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.51,0:09:40.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上流小姐  有只水母堵住了你耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:40.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lady Upturn, there's a jellyfish blocking your ears
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.35,0:09:43.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:43.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, goodness
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.14,0:09:48.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定是我在水母田散步时就蜇上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:45.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It must have gotten stuck up there
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:48.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,during my walk through Jellyfish Fields
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.02,0:09:55.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他真实的音乐水平就这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:55.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that what he really sounds like?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.53,0:10:00.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这音乐太难听了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:10:00.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This music is terrible
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.08,0:10:02.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:02.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.08,0:10:05.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母的嗡嗡声一定是改变了噪音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:05.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The jellyfish's buzzing must have altered the noise
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.16,0:10:07.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你才会觉得好听
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:07.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to be more pleasurable for you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.55,0:10:16.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不许再吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:16.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop that racket
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.34,0:10:17.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:17.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.88,0:10:20.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你竟敢打断我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:20.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How dare you interrupt m--
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.14,0:10:22.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有话要向大家坦白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:22.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a confession to make
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.64,0:10:26.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有只水母堵住了我的耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:26.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A jellyfish was obstructing my ears
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.93,0:10:30.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因此我并没有真正听到这骗子的音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:30.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I hadn't truly heard this fraud's music
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.60,0:10:33.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然我已经听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:33.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now that I have
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.07,0:10:35.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就冒犯到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:35.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am offended
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.74,0:10:40.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为弥补这糟糕演奏给各位带来的伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:40.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To make up for this abysmal performance
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.57,0:10:43.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想邀请各位回到我家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:43.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would like to invite you all back to my home
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,体验真正的音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to experience real music
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.24,0:10:47.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,演奏者是我最新的艺术家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:47.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by my newest artiste
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.45,0:10:50.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,音乐大师派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:50.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maestro Patrick Star
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.08,0:10:50.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:50.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:11:01.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(886,894)}蛋黄酱
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.12,0:11:25.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:25.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Encore
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.16,0:11:26.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:26.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.54,0:11:29.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们还想听
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:29.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We want more
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.29,0:11:30.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:30.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you really mean it?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.92,0:11:32.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:32.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.29,0:11:34.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们有水母
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:34.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.84,0:11:37.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知足吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:37.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take what I can get
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.93,0:11:42.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.93,0:11:42.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Squidward
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:50.35,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}天外来章
