Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:57.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(656,544)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:57.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:12:07.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1710,806)}裤头村新闻
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.61,0:12:01.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最新消息  新证据表明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:01.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This just in: New evidence that
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.70,0:12:04.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不明飞行物已秘密造访
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:03.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,unidentified flying objects
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:04.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,have been secretly visiting
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.91,0:12:07.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村长达数年
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:07.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikini Bottom for years
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.20,0:12:07.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上将
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:07.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,General
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.99,0:12:11.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些照片与视频造假的概率有多大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:10.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what are the chances that these photos
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:11.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and videos are just a hoax?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.16,0:12:16.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,99.99999%
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:16.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,99.99999%
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.88,0:12:18.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,情况就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:18.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you have it--
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.09,0:12:19.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真凭实据表明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:19.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,conclusive proof
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.38,0:12:25.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞碟有0.00001%的概率是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:25.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that there is a 0.00001% chance UFOs are real
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.97,0:12:29.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说飞碟的证据可能无处不在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:29.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That means there could be evidence of UFOs anywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.64,0:12:32.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:32.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go find some
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外星人快来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, alien
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.06,0:12:37.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:37.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alien
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.08,0:12:56.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都已经大半夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:56.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the middle of the night
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.00,0:12:58.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个白痴在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:58.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you two idiots doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.42,0:13:01.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们找到了外星人怪圈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:01.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We found an alien crop circle
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,之所以有怪圈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's only a crop circle
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.30,0:13:05.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全是因为你们乱踩我秋海棠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:05.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because you're stomping on my begonias
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.05,0:13:08.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:08.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.89,0:13:10.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  就我们踩的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:10.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that is us
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.56,0:13:13.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们在找外星人和飞碟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:13.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're hunting space aliens and UFOs
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.52,0:13:17.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本就没有外星人跟飞碟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:17.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Space aliens and UFOs do not exist
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.81,0:13:19.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我去睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:19.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go to sleep
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.74,0:13:31.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:31.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.24,0:13:33.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们想看外星人是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:33.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want to see space aliens?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.66,0:13:36.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就给你们看外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:36.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll show you space aliens
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.96,0:13:40.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这东西很有可能就是飞碟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:40.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This could definitely be a UFO
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.13,0:13:46.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的是飞碟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:46.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A real UFO
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.59,0:13:50.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一类接触
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:50.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First contact
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.73,0:13:57.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好星际
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:57.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Intergalactic
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好太空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spacey
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.60,0:13:59.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:13:59.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cosmic
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.78,0:14:11.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们刚被个飞碟给撞了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:11.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We just got hit by a flying saucer
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.08,0:14:12.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:12.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.99,0:14:14.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,酷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:14.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cool
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.54,0:14:16.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好  地球生物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:16.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Greetings, earthlings
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.12,0:14:19.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是真的外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:19.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A r-r-real space alien
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.13,0:14:21.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:21.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Greetings, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我扮的  你们俩戴锡纸的白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's me, you tinfoil twits
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.80,0:14:27.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一直都是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:27.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was all me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.63,0:14:30.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本就没有外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:30.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Space aliens don't exist
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.26,0:14:31.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:31.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.85,0:14:34.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:34.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.01,0:14:36.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们现在能明白自己有多傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:36.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can see now how silly we really were
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.27,0:14:39.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:39.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.19,0:14:41.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,改扮超级英雄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:41.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's play superheroes instead
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.15,0:14:41.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:41.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.98,0:14:44.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码超级英雄确实是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:44.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least we know they're real
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.15,0:14:49.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:49.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Idiots
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.79,0:15:04.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:04.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At last
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.09,0:15:07.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们远古水下祖先存在的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:07.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,evidence of our ancient aquatic ancestors
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.80,0:15:10.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要把文物带回飞船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:10.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We must take the artifact back to the ship
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.38,0:15:11.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会发大财
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:11.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll be rich
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.34,0:15:12.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,发个大财
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:12.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rich, I say
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.18,0:15:17.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早跟你们俩说了  根本没有外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:17.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you two, space aliens don't exist
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.93,0:15:19.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:19.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go away
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.35,0:15:21.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:21.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.52,0:15:25.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,文物被寄生虫寄生了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:25.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The artifact is infested with a parasite
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.19,0:15:28.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须先把它消杀了才可以出发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:28.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We must eradicate it before our departure
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.07,0:15:31.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我告诉你  这东西可难搞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:31.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, it's always something
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.79,0:15:43.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:43.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who--
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.33,0:15:44.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:44.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who's there?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.57,0:16:11.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:11.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My holes
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.36,0:16:13.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:13.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My holes
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.12,0:16:19.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢海神王  我还有阅读眼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:19.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank Neptune I have my readers
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:21.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1422,252)}老练的头脑
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.42,0:16:27.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝跟派大星是走火入魔了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:27.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have SpongeBob and Patrick gone cuckoo?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.05,0:16:31.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:31.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.60,0:16:37.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝还有派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:37.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob and Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.85,0:16:39.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把你们这破面具摘了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:39.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,take off those stupid masks
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.77,0:16:41.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:41.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know it's you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.56,0:16:44.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:44.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.31,0:16:45.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你快伤到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:45.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're hurting me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.77,0:16:47.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:47.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mayday
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.40,0:16:48.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们需要支援
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:48.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We need backup
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:54.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1282,248)}加入蟹堡王团队
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.99,0:16:57.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个在里面能不能闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:57.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you two shut up in there?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.41,0:16:59.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还想把你们脑袋给
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:16:59.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to get your heads--
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.16,0:17:01.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摘了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:01.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,off?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.12,0:17:06.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那俩白痴还真是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:06.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those nimrods were right
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.04,0:17:07.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的有外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:07.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aliens are real
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.92,0:17:13.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  放我进去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:13.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, let me in
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.76,0:17:14.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:14.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You were right
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.97,0:17:18.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,转告派大星  你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:18.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell Patrick you were right
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.47,0:17:19.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:19.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Success
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.72,0:17:22.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,害虫撤离了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:22.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The vermin has evacuated
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.31,0:17:24.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来把文物带上飞船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:24.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's take the artifact to our ship
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.39,0:17:27.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免得那只可怕臭虫又回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:27.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before that horrible stinkbug comes back
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.87,0:17:44.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:44.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.45,0:17:45.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:45.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.25,0:17:46.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别走别走别走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:46.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.60,0:18:05.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我就说  这就给你见识牵引光束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:05.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So I says, I'll show you a tractor beam
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.19,0:18:11.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里到底谁管事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:11.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, who's in charge here?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.90,0:18:14.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要跟经理说话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:14.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to speak to the manager
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.44,0:18:15.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,经理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:15.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Manager?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.95,0:18:19.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带我去找你们的领导
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:19.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take me to your leader
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.12,0:18:22.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那叫指导
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:22.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That would be our supervisor
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.49,0:18:24.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他办公室就在走廊里面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:24.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,His office is down this hall
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.08,0:18:25.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要先左转再右转
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:25.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just make a left then a right
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.54,0:18:26.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别跟他说话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:26.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't talk to him
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.96,0:18:29.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就是我们消杀的害虫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:29.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He is the vermin we eradicated
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.92,0:18:33.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来有谁消杀课挂科了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:33.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like somebody failed eradication class
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.17,0:18:36.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:36.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Zip it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是你俩的上级
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I outrank you both
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.80,0:18:42.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要你们把我家从哪找来就放回哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:42.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want you to put my home back where you found it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.18,0:18:43.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能往前靠近点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:43.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could you step forward?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.89,0:18:45.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听不清
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:45.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm hard of hearing
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.68,0:18:46.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:46.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.60,0:18:47.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:47.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And another thing
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.85,0:18:50.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们干什么要来地球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:50.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the big idea of coming to my planet
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.65,0:18:53.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在我家庭院直接拐走我家房子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:53.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and taking my house out of my yard
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.52,0:18:55.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就因为它样子就像你们的呆头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:55.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just because it looked like your stupid head?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.11,0:19:02.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会讲话的害虫危害最大了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:02.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Talking vermin are the worst kind
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.87,0:19:03.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说得对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:03.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.83,0:19:05.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为了稍微弥补一点损失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:05.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just so it's not a total loss
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.99,0:19:10.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,建议咱们做点检查  来给它探测一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:10.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I say we run some tests and do a probe
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.58,0:19:11.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:11.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.71,0:19:13.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要探测了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:13.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're doing a probe
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.75,0:19:17.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,探测
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:17.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Probe
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:17.67,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(896,386)}探测
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.38,0:19:19.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,探测
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:19.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Probe?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.27,0:19:31.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,X光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:31.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,X-ray
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.85,0:19:35.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然头盖骨很大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:35.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Despite the large cranium
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.02,0:19:37.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但大脑的尺寸似乎低于平均水平
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:37.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the brain seems below average size
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.11,0:19:41.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,高血压
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:41.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,High blood pressure
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.78,0:19:43.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好小心一下脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:43.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Better watch that temper
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.99,0:19:46.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,转动脖子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:46.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rotate neck
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.96,0:19:55.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往鼻子塞水管
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:55.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nose hose
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.34,0:20:06.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,存储空间了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:06.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Impressive storage space
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.81,0:20:09.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在来做最有趣的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:09.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now for the fun part
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.94,0:20:18.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:18.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Freedom
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.18,0:20:50.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:50.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.79,0:21:17.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:17.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.63,0:21:19.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托不要探测我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:19.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please don't probe me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.52,0:21:35.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这项探测要问的是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:35.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In this probe, I will be asking you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.44,0:21:38.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有关你童年的尴尬问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:38.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,embarrassing questions about your childhood
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.94,0:21:43.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我应该确实不擅长交友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.94,0:21:43.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I did have trouble making friends
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.44,0:21:47.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,发泄很多被压抑的记忆之后
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.20,0:21:48.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后三岁时  我说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:48.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then when I was three, I said
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.91,0:21:50.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈咪  早告诉过你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.91,0:21:50.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Mumsy, I told you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.24,0:21:51.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢海草汁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:51.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't like kelp juice"
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.74,0:21:54.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她就说  别管我叫妈咪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:54.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And she said, "Well, I don't like being called Mumsy"
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.54,0:21:54.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:54.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.12,0:21:57.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.12,0:21:57.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enough
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.84,0:22:07.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚吧  害虫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:07.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good riddance, vermin
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.59,0:22:10.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笨文物你自己留着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:10.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep your dumb, old artifact
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.30,0:22:12.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你妈的故事也自己憋着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.30,0:22:12.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you can keep your mother stories too
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.97,0:22:14.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.97,0:22:14.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oy vey
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.06,0:22:18.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  不知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:18.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, if I didn't know better
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.77,0:22:22.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还以为那真的是飞船呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:22.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd be thinking that was a real alien spaceship
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.02,0:22:24.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我们可知道了  对吧章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.02,0:22:24.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we do know better, huh, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.57,0:22:26.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我错了  行不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.57,0:22:26.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was wrong, okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.44,0:22:28.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的有外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.44,0:22:28.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aliens are real
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.11,0:22:29.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来在他们飞船上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.11,0:22:29.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was on their ship
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.49,0:22:31.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟他们讲我妈的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.49,0:22:31.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I was telling them about my mother
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.37,0:22:32.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.37,0:22:32.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and--
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.24,0:22:33.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们都懂  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.24,0:22:33.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We get it, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.99,0:22:36.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本没有外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:36.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aliens don't exist
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.08,0:22:38.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可真的有外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:38.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But they do exist
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.71,0:22:41.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.71,0:22:41.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
